OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fwill move inland, perhaps a little
OL,7,Fdrizzle over the hills by dawn. Best
OL,8,Fof the clear skies through Deeside and
OL,9,Fwinds remaining light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FMuch of the low cloud should
OL,12,Fclear during the morning, but it could
OL,13,Fbe rather persistent through northern
OL,14,FAberdeenshire. Light or moderate north
OL,15,For northwest winds. Feeling a bit
OL,16,Fcooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
